author: stefan2
msg: On the authzperf branch:  Boost config file parsing.
Instead of fiddling with individual bytes, let the parser fetch whole
lines from the buffer and process these.
* subversion/libsvn_subr/config_file.c
(parse_context_t): Add another temporary for the current line. Not
all parse_* functions will need it but some do.
(parser_get_line): New parser function, similar to skip_to_eoln.
(parse_value): Superceded by ...
(parse_value_continuation_lines): ... this one reading whole lines
excluding the first of a value.
(parse_option,
parse_section_name): Parse line-by-line instead of char-by-char.
(svn_config__parse_stream): Initialize the new context element.
